\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 There is no analogous technology in ebooks, so the conversion will usually end up placing the image either centered or floating close to the point in the text where it was }{\rtlch\f1 \i \cf10 \fs24 inserted\i0 }{\rtlch\f1 \fs24 , not necessarily where it appears on the page in Word.}\par
